cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NI 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on modeling the early visual system and its ability to integrate contours. 
2. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also likely as the paper discusses the role of recurrent and feedback connections in neural processing. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses a combination of Predictive Coding and Sparse Coding to develop the model. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses a model that can process context-dependent information, which is a key aspect of AI. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the least likely category as the paper does not focus on networking or internet architecture.
